snippet.title: BLACK CATS are so HARDCORE - It's TIME FOR YOU to LAUGH!
snippet.description:
Cats are the best animals. They make us laugh all the time. Here's a special compilation about black cats! I'm sure that you will laugh your head off! The hardest try not to laugh challenge ever! Just look at all these black cats and kittens how they fail, behave, meow, spin, beg... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
